dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights. Geodetic reference system: ETRF 2000 (2008.0). "Sistema di riferimento geodetico ETRF2000 (2008.0) rappresentazione cartografica RDN2008 Italy Zone (EPSG 6875) altimetria in metri riferita al livello medio del mare". Includes sources of mapping. Map shows administrative boundaries. The international and local administrative boundaries are not official.
